short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Automatically refresh your session on UNSW Moodle.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Having to relogin to Moodle every ten minutes has driven me up the wall. This extension refreshes your UNSW Moodle session every ten minutes by creating and closing a tab. You have to already be logged in on UNSW SSO.
